data.caption: Announcement under Regulation 30 (LODR)-Analyst / Investor Meet - Outcome
data.news_body: In furtherance to our intimation letter dated 28th July, 2023 with respect to the convening of Investors / Analyst conference call 'Earning Call' on Wednesday, 02nd August, 2023 from 16:00 hrs IST onwards for discussing the financial results of the Company for the quarter ended 30th June, 2023, in this regard we inform you that the Company held Investors / Analysts call today at Wednesday, 02nd August, 2023. Summary highlights: Q1 Consolidated Total Income is Rs. 374.85 crores Q1 Consolidated EBITDA is Rs. 100.55 crores Q1 Consolidated PAT stood at Rs. 63.72 crores Q1 Consolidated throughput increased 0.69% to 179,897 TEUsConsolidated financials for the quarter ended 30th June, 2023The audio transcript of the Q1 FY 2023-24 Conference Call has been uploaded on the website at: https://www.gatewaydistriparks.com/audio-recording.php  The transcript for the said call shall be shared with the Stock Exchanges and will also be uploaded Company's website (www.gatewaydistriparks.com) in due course. Kindly take the information on record.

data.caption: Outcome Of Board Meeting Financial Results For The Year Ended March 31St , 2023
data.news_body:
Pursuant to the applicable provisions of SEBI (Listing Obligations and Disclosure Requirements) Regulations, 2015 (Listing Regulations), including Regulation 30 & 33, this is to inform you that the Board of Directors of Gateway Distriparks Limited, at their meeting held today, i.e. Friday, 26th May, 2023 approved the Audited standalone and consolidated financial results for the quarter and year ended 31st March, 2023.

The Audited standalone and consolidated financial results for the quarter and financial year ended March 31, 2023 along with Independent Auditors Report thereon issued by M/s S.R.Batliboi and Co.LLP, Chartered Accountants are enclosed herewith.

The Board meeting commenced at 1.25 p.m. and concluded at 2:25 p.m.
